msg: Refactored RelationExtractorAnnotator into an abstract class to allow sharing of code among several Relation Extraction analysis engines.  NamedEntityPairRelationExtractorAnnotator is now the analysis engine for tagging relations between two entities and DegreeOfRelationExtractorAnnotator will mark pairs of modifiers and entities with the Degree_Of relation.
